"product3":{"title":"Styling","description":"I make sure my hair is sectioned in four, then I apply the Olive Miracle leave-in conditioner to damp hair, followed by Castor oil hair treatment with mink oil. Depending on what style I’d do, I’ll start it. Ex: After my hair is moisturized, I’ll do a twist out and leave it in.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/75691a5cb5fa2ddeebae71c4ec8fca8c/africanprideleavein.jpg"},"productURL":"https://www.amazon.com/African-Pride-Miracle-Leave-Conditioner/dp/B00N0YXL4K"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/a307317990559cae79a3f37a0c8f8453/hollywoodbeautycastoroil.jpg"},"productURL":"https://www.amazon.com/Hollywood-Beauty-Castor-Treatment-Ounce/dp/B00TJ6P6XM"}]},"instagrammer":"@henribstyles","author":"@nicemarcela","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/d3ef745b77ea9a8ee2c26aaa7b38211b/ee604/henrib1.png","srcSet":"/static/d3ef745b77ea9a8ee2c26aaa7b38211b/69585/henrib1.png 200w,\n/static/d3ef745b77ea9a8ee2c26aaa7b38211b/497c6/henrib1.png 400w,\n/static/d3ef745b77ea9a8ee2c26aaa7b38211b/ee604/henrib1.png 800w,\n/static/d3ef745b77ea9a8ee2c26aaa7b38211b/05d05/henrib1.png 1080w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"confidence-queen-henri-b-talks-about-her-career-as-a-musician-and-her-haircare-while-playing-with-different-hairstyles"},"excerpt":"Henri is a musician from Silver Spring, Maryland. She is of Ghanian descent, both parents from Guinea Conakry. She defines herself as…"}},{"node":{"id":"9322163b-0a68-5388-bfe0-18231bb03133","frontmatter":{"linkURL":"https://www.instagram.com/nicemarcela/","instaURL":"https://www.instagram.com/meltifaceted/","title":"How Melissa Mel is creating space for small businesses with the WoMi™️ App.","type":"Hair Type: 3A/3B/3C","tags":["Interview"],"date":"Jul 3rd 2021","product1":{"title":"Cleansing","description":"Wash with Rizos Curls Shampoo, massaging tf out of my scalp & rinse.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/831e17333d1819e3279df8fc9827e54d/rizoscurlsshampoo.png"},"productURL":"https://rizoscurls.com/collections/haircare/products/hydrating-shampoo"}]},"product2":{"title":"Conditioning","description":"Condition with Rizos Curls Conditioner, massage & leave in for duration of shower before rinsing.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/ddf9982476703217b2468d53de964869/rizoscurlsconditioner.png"},"productURL":"https://rizoscurls.com/collections/haircare/products/deep-conditioner"}]},"product3":{"title":"Styling","description":"Scrunch in plenty of Rizos Curls Curl Defining cream and lightly diffuse for volume. I add in Rizos Curls gel if I am pinning a side back & to lay down curly side burns & baby hairs.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/a5147de3ffcd84ff014a2512c8615d68/rizoscurlsdefiningcream.png"},"productURL":"https://rizoscurls.com/products/curl-defining-cream"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/e817f657c75552e88d72881e76679908/rizoscurlsgel.png"},"productURL":"https://rizoscurls.com/collections/haircare/products/light-hold-gel"}]},"instagrammer":"@meltifaceted","author":"@nicemarcela","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/674ad32df5437221e0d078aa1424f490/ee604/melissamel1.png","srcSet":"/static/674ad32df5437221e0d078aa1424f490/69585/melissamel1.png 200w,\n/static/674ad32df5437221e0d078aa1424f490/497c6/melissamel1.png 400w,\n/static/674ad32df5437221e0d078aa1424f490/ee604/melissamel1.png 800w,\n/static/674ad32df5437221e0d078aa1424f490/12892/melissamel1.png 1078w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"how-melissa-mel-is-creating-space-for-small-businesses-with-the-womi-app"},"excerpt":"Melissa Mel is a multifaceted creative entrepreneur based in California, she is the creator of the WoMi™️ App, a directory of Woman owned…"}},{"node":{"id":"ece139d5-5a67-5ce4-b544-57ee6a8e6f86","frontmatter":{"linkURL":"https://www.instagram.com/nicemarcela/","instaURL":"https://www.instagram.com/curlymonaa/","title":"Vegan and cruelty-free curls: How digital creator, Ramona achieves bouncy curls using vegan products.","type":"Hair Type: 2C/3A","tags":["Interview"],"date":"Jun 5th 2021","product1":{"title":"Cleansing","description":"I cleanse my hair about 3 times every washday with Curly Secret Hello Fresh Hair Shampoo because, at the first time, all the greasiness, dirt, and oils are coming off the scalp. By the third time, I am sure that my scalp is clean enough. I use a scalp massaging brush to stimulate the blood flow and to loosen up any dirt. Then I rinse it out with warm water. Once a month I clarify with Curly Secret Deep Clean Shampoo.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/0005848025885a866b32d7b99c36300f/curlysecretshampoo.png"},"productURL":"https://www.curlysecret.com/products/hello-fresh-hair-shampoo"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/058d8dc6ee0a57a81d3e56471694ef08/curlysecretdeepshampoo.png"},"productURL":"https://www.curlysecret.com/products/deep-cleansing-shampoo-1"}]},"product2":{"title":"Conditioning","description":"I never actually use conditioner, I immediately deep condition my hair with the Shea Moisture Deep conditioner (fruit fusion) after shampooing because, in my opinion, conditioners do not do much other than detangling the hair and weight down my hair. I do not apply the deep conditioner to my roots as this will leave me with greasy hair within 3 days. I mix my deep conditioners with one teaspoon of olaplex N°3 and then leave it on for 20 minutes. I rinse it out with either cold or warm water. It depends on my mood.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/58bfa9f4c2b0b8c41b34121ea0077ec1/sheamoisturefruitfusionmask.jpg"},"productURL":"https://www.amazon.com/Shea-Moisture-Fusion-Coconut-Weightless/dp/B01AVHXIHS"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/3dd2a035b02464db163b530ed34acb20/olaplex3.jpg"},"productURL":"https://olaplex.com/products/olaplex-no-3-hair-perfector"}]},"product3":{"title":"Styling","description":"I use one to two styling products and I use it on soaking wet hair. I brush my hair upside down and brush my hair away from the scalp with my Denman brush. Then I rake the Curly Secret Reviving Leave-in in and scrunch, scrunch, scrunch! Then I take a microfiber towel and scrunch the excess water out. After that, I apply the Curly Secret Hemp & Flaxseeds gel or Curly Secret Volumizing Foam by scrunching it in my hair. Sometimes I glaze a mousse in and then scrunch. After that, I diffuse it on low speed/medium heat.","gallery":[{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/9255d30f68dddb718c64f0b1d0647713/curlysecretleavein.png"},"productURL":"https://www.curlysecret.com/products/curl-reviving-leave-in"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/ed67ebc3edada983ce9b11d4619aae11/curlysecretflaxseedsgel.png"},"productURL":"https://www.curlysecret.com/products/flaxseed-hemp-seed-styling-gel"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/8d5a77d828967e4db1398bf913a5ae90/curlysecretfoam.png"},"productURL":"https://www.curlysecret.com/products/volumizing-curl-foam"},{"image":{"publicURL":"/static/792eb2b1036f3921d95070c063ce293f/denmanbrush.jpg"},"productURL":"https://denmanbrushus.com/products/d3-original-styler-7-row?variant=31964917334100"}]},"instagrammer":"@curlymonaa","author":"@nicemarcela","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/1d30a3a1c8d967939d4350f9c8a74285/ee604/ramona.png","srcSet":"/static/1d30a3a1c8d967939d4350f9c8a74285/69585/ramona.png 200w,\n/static/1d30a3a1c8d967939d4350f9c8a74285/497c6/ramona.png 400w,\n/static/1d30a3a1c8d967939d4350f9c8a74285/ee604/ramona.png 800w,\n/static/1d30a3a1c8d967939d4350f9c8a74285/05d05/ramona.png 1080w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"vegan-and-cruelty-free-curls-how-digital-creator-ramona-achieves-bouncy-curls-using-vegan-products"},"excerpt":"Ramona is a veterinary assistant from the Netherlands, and a digital creator on Instagram, where she shares her routine and 2C/3A curls…"}}]}}}